        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Reinvigorating American Energy Infrastructure Act</b></p> <p>This bill expands eligibility for the Department of Energy's loan guarantee program for advanced fossil energy technology projects to include certain high efficiency, low emissions coal-fired power plants.</p>]]></text>
